And it took me a year
and a half to edit.

00:21:43.970 --> 00:21:48.730
Right. Patina took a year,
almost a year to write.

00:21:48.730 --> 00:21:50.030
Every book is a little
bit different.

00:21:50.030 --> 00:21:51.330
You never really know.

00:21:51.330 --> 00:21:52.630
I just kind of sit down
and do the best I can.

00:21:52.630 --> 00:21:54.090
But some books take
a little bit --

00:21:54.090 --> 00:21:56.080
I mean, All American Boys
took six weeks, you know.

00:21:56.080 --> 00:21:57.770
It just kind of depends
on what the book is, man.

00:21:57.770 --> 00:22:00.130
Every book's different.

00:22:00.130 --> 00:22:03.910
&gt;&gt; So how many books
did you write down?

00:22:03.910 --> 00:22:06.220
&gt;&gt; Jason Reynolds: How many
books did I write down?

00:22:06.220 --> 00:22:08.270
How many books have I written?

00:22:08.270 --> 00:22:10.850
I think we're at number
12, something like that.

00:22:10.850 --> 00:22:13.250
I don't know, 12, 13.

00:22:13.250 --> 00:22:15.000
We're up there somewhere.

00:22:15.000 --> 00:22:16.520
I just do my work, I
ain't worried about it.

00:22:16.520 --> 00:22:19.640
Just keep it going, you know.

00:22:19.640 --> 00:22:20.940
&gt;&gt; Okay.

00:22:20.940 --> 00:22:23.500
&gt;&gt; In your opinion what is
the scariest sea creature?

00:22:23.500 --> 00:22:25.050
&gt;&gt; Jason Reynolds: In my
opinion what is the scariest

00:22:25.050 --> 00:22:26.590
sea creature?

00:22:26.590 --> 00:22:28.160
Any sea creature I can't see.

00:22:28.160 --> 00:22:29.460
[laughter].

00:22:29.460 --> 00:22:33.660
For sure. Yeah.

00:22:33.660 --> 00:22:38.540
&gt;&gt; I have read all of the Track
series books except for Lu

00:22:38.540 --> 00:22:42.440
because it isn't, you
know, released yet.

00:22:42.440 --> 00:22:43.740
&gt;&gt; Jason Reynolds: Yeah.

00:22:43.740 --> 00:22:49.190
&gt;&gt; But how do you think Lu
will like as a story play out?

00:22:49.190 --> 00:22:50.490
&gt;&gt; Jason Reynolds:
So you want me

00:22:50.490 --> 00:22:51.790
to tell you what the book is --

00:22:51.790 --> 00:22:53.090
you want me to break
it all down for you?

00:22:53.090 --> 00:22:54.390
[laughter].

